=Introduction=

Basic Requirement is an addon to manage and apply requirements on your capella models.
It shall not be confused with requirement-vp and only provides basic requirement capabilities:

* Definition of Requirements
* Requirement Wizard to apply requirements on Capella Elements 
* Integration with Capella's Trace Manager
* Visualization of requirement tables

